Package: SelectPie
Type: Package
Title: MLE for Compositional Models with Sample Selection
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("First", "Last", email = "you@email.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Maximum likelihood estimation for compositional outcome models
    that account for selection into the sample using a bivariate extreme
    value (Gumbel-logistic) copula. Provides the core estimator SelectPie(),
    supporting helpers for the bivariate EVD integral and marginal CDF, and
    a utility for exporting results to LaTeX tables.
